<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />You water its furrows abundantly;</para>

<para style="q1">you settle down the furrows' ridges;</para>

<para style="q1">you make them soft with rain showers;</para>

<para style="q1">you bless the sprouts between them.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="11" style="v" />You crown the year with your goodness;</para>

<para style="q1">the tracks behind your chariot drop fatness down to the earth.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />The pastures in the wilderness drip with dew,</para>

<para style="q1">and the hills are clothed with joy.</para>
